release_note: We fixed the bug that the app display Consent GDPR dialog again and again on some users.
We fixed the bug that the app cannot be scrolled.
We fixed the bug that the app cannot be scrolled.

You can now select the HTML file format when exporting data. You can narrow down the search by multiple words. You can delete the diary for the specified period of time. You can add a diary by pressing and holding the date on the calendar. Fixed an error in iCloud backup function. Fixed some other bugs.

Autosave when going to background while editing log Introduced line breaks for easier editing when multiple images are inserted Fixed some crash errors Fixed an issue where iCloud backup may not work well
Bug fixes. Theme color settings Entry scroll

New fonts added Can now select photos from all folders when selecting The fine size of the list screen has been adjusted well Fixed error when exporting log data Fixed the issue of not being able to operate with the new iPad Pro Some other minor issues have been fixed
